Required packages for GUI modules.

Debian install
==============

apt-get install libxml2-dev libboost-all-dev libssl-dev libncurses5\
                libpython2.7 python-dbus-dev python-libxml2 python-numpy\
                python-m2crypto libghc-opengl-dev libqt4-dev libqt4-opengl-dev\
                libqtwebkit-dev libmysqlclient-dev mysql-server flex cmake\
                cmake-qt-gui cmake-curses-gui build-essential libcdio-dev

                
Ubuntu install 14.04
====================
xutils-dev libxml2-dev libboost-all-dev python-all-dev libssl-dev libncurses5-dev\
           libhdf5-dev libqt4-dev libqt4-opengl-dev\
           libqtwebkit-dev libmysqlclient-dev mysql-server flex cmake\
           cmake-curses-gui build-essential python-sphinx
           
